This directory contains docker files for creating a Macaulay2 image:

```
DOCKER_BUILDKIT=1 docker build \
    --build-arg MACAULAY2_RPM=Macaulay2.rpm \
    -t pzinn/m2container .
```

The rpm file for Macaulay2 must be manually put in the same directory as the Dockerfile.
Set `MACAULAY2_RPM` to its filename.
